            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "。 Path 4: P -> C3 -> C2 -> C5): \\(30\\%\\) \\(\\star\\) \\(7\\%\\) \\(\\star\\) \\(35\\% = 0.735\\%\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "list",
            "bbox": [
                0.224,
